The file `measat_releaseX1.8.hex` in this directory is firmware for the
Agilent/Keysight 82357B USB-to-GPIB adapter.

It is redistributed here unmodified from the upstream project at
https://github.com/fmhess/linux_gpib_firmware, which in turn obtained
it from Agilent/Keysight. The firmware itself is proprietary; its
redistribution is permitted as part of drivers that operate the
hardware. See the upstream repository's README files for the full
redistribution context.

This LICENSE notice applies only to the firmware blob in this directory.
The rest of the ugpibd source tree is GPL-3.0-or-later.
